app.cash.inject.inflation

Class InflationInjectFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • app.cash.inject.inflation.InflationInjectFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.view.LayoutInflater.Factory, android.view.LayoutInflater.Factory2

    public final class InflationInjectFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.view.LayoutInflater.Factory2
    A factory for LayoutInflater which can create @InflationInject-annotated views. This type should be injected rather than created manually as it will ask your dependency graph for a map of all the creatable views.
    See Also:
    InflationInject, InflationModule
